102  private static long RunBenchmark(GameObject gameObject) {
103  var ticks = new List<long>();
104 
105  // run the tests
106  for (int i = 0; i < TestRuns; ++i) {
107  var stopwatch = new System.Diagnostics.Stopwatch();
108  stopwatch.Start();
109  var spawned = Object.Instantiate(gameObject);
110  stopwatch.Stop();
111  ticks.Add(stopwatch.ElapsedTicks);
112  Object.DestroyImmediate(spawned);
113  }
114 
115  // compute the average
116  long total = 0;
117  foreach (long tick in ticks) {
118  total += tick;
119  }
120  return total / ticks.Count;
121  }
122  }
